summary: This file defines a Vue component named EducationComponent, which displays educational information including degrees and certifications from different institutions.
functionality: The main functionality of this file is to render educational details in a structured format, using the EducationItem component to display individual educational items.
relationships: It imports and uses the EducationItem component to display individual educational items.
It uses styles from ../assets/main.scss for styling the component.
It might be used in a larger profile or resume section of the application.

identified_relationships.description: EducationComponent imports and uses the EducationItem component to display individual educational items.
EducationComponent references educationData.js to fetch and display educational information such as degrees and certifications.
EducationComponent references global.css for styling purposes to ensure consistent styling across the component.
EducationComponent references the Vuex store to access and manage state related to educational information.
